16 (2010)</a></span></div></div></li><li><div class="item-wrapper"><div class="menu-link"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php/en/%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%85%D0%B8%D0%B2%D0%B01/systasis-15-2009">Systasis 15 (2009)</a></span></div></div></li><li><div class="item-wrapper"><div class="menu-link"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php/en/%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%85%D0%B8%D0%B2%D0%B01/systasis-14-2009">Systasis 14 (2009</a></span></div></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><ul class="submenu accordionSub" style="display: block;"><span style="font-size: x-small;"></span><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a class="acc60" href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=51&amp;Itemid=60&amp;lang=en">Systasis 1 (2002)</a></span></li><span style="font-size: x-small;"></span><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a class="acc61" href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=62&amp;Itemid=61&amp;lang=en">Systasis 2-3 (2003)</a></span></li><span style="font-size: x-small;"></span><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a class="acc72" href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=88&amp;Itemid=72&amp;lang=en">Systasis 4-5 (2004)</a></span></li><span style="font-size: x-small;"></span><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a class="acc69" href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=106&amp;Itemid=69&amp;lang=en">Systasis 6-7 (2005)</a></span></li><span style="font-size: x-small;"></span><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a class="acc70" href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=98&amp;Itemid=70&amp;lang=en">Systasis 8-9 (2006)</a></span></li><span style="font-size: x-small;"></span><li><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a class="acc71" href="http://www.systasis.org/index.php?option=com_content&amp;v